casebody.data:
MOONELIS et al., Appellants, v. SMITH, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. January 12, 1894.) Action by Adolph Moonelis and another against James E. Smith.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and PARKER, JJ.

Mr. Arnold, for appellants. E. W. S. Johnston, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
